Covid-19 opportunity for Japan-South Korea to work together: Yomiuri Shimbun 
South Korea's President Moon Jae-in waves a South Korean flag during a ceremony to mark the March 1st Independence Movement against Japanese colonial rule in Seoul on March 1, 2020. South Korea's President Moon Jae-in waves a South Korean flag during a ceremony to mark the March 1st Independence Movement against Japanese colonial rule in Seoul on March 1, 2020. PHOTO: AFP 
Published 
Mar 5, 2020, 11:00 am SGT 
